usage:

rcvface <facehost> [<relay>]
  facehost: name/addr of face detector
  relay: relay addr [optional]

face [<dev>] [<relay>]
  dev: video device number [0-3]; default 0
  relay: optional relay host

(alternatively, face can get relay address from FACERELAY environmenet variable)

zproxy can be used as a relay if direct connection between detector and receiver is unavailable


dependencies:
OpenCV 3.2  http://opencv.org/downloads.html

Zeromq 4.2  http://zeromq.org

on OSX:
 brew tap homebrew/science; brew install opencv3 zeromq

